---

## ðŸ”¹ System Architecture
1. **Input Methods:** Users can interact through **voice, text, and image uploads**.
2. **Processing Unit:** AI models process the input using **Computer Vision and NLP**.
3. **Output Generation:** The system provides **real-time responses, navigation assistance, and medical insights**.

